  "detailed_description": "Play as Hauntii, a naïve ghost on a journey to ascend beyond the afterlife. Explore with your angelic partner, solve challenges, and collect starry fragments to reveal glimpses of your past life. Use the unique <i>Haunt</i> mechanic to possess and take control over almost anything (even trees)! Dash, jump, blast, glide and shake your way through the intricate world of <i>Eternity</i>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/f88757cae69ed51a1c692ec16ec4d9f2.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/f88757cae69ed51a1c692ec16ec4d9f2.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Haunt</h2> As a ghost, use your haunting powers to command both creatures and the environment itself. <br>Craft an array of solutions to puzzles, and devise various approaches to combat scenarios.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/5b18aa5f4b202fabf0a0de4121d0fae0.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/5b18aa5f4b202fabf0a0de4121d0fae0.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2> An expansive hand-crafted world, with tight yet open-ended environments. Whichever path you take, there'll always be something around the corner, waiting to be discovered.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/93c1aeeb9b55a892600263fc0c7ae08b.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/93c1aeeb9b55a892600263fc0c7ae08b.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect</h2> Build the Constellations and uncover the story of Hauntii's past life. Find the pieces you'll need by exploring, solving challenges, and trading with other ghosts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/d87e29998f25aa44b5a7a3e9209eaab8.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/d87e29998f25aa44b5a7a3e9209eaab8.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/68e14f7ba65c2e5e4e195605cdfa9a91.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=125 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/68e14f7ba65c2e5e4e195605cdfa9a91.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game employs a unique hand-crafted art style, making use of line art, animation and a striking two-tone palette. <br>Meanwhile, Hauntii’s dynamic soundtrack sways and swells with the action on-screen, creating a captivating audiovisual experience.",
  "about_the_game": "Play as Hauntii, a naïve ghost on a journey to ascend beyond the afterlife. Explore with your angelic partner, solve challenges, and collect starry fragments to reveal glimpses of your past life. Use the unique <i>Haunt</i> mechanic to possess and take control over almost anything (even trees)! Dash, jump, blast, glide and shake your way through the intricate world of <i>Eternity</i>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/f88757cae69ed51a1c692ec16ec4d9f2.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/f88757cae69ed51a1c692ec16ec4d9f2.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Haunt</h2> As a ghost, use your haunting powers to command both creatures and the environment itself. <br>Craft an array of solutions to puzzles, and devise various approaches to combat scenarios.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/5b18aa5f4b202fabf0a0de4121d0fae0.poster.avif?t=1773681682\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/5b18aa5f4b202fabf0a0de4121d0fae0.webm?t=1773681682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2> An expansive hand-crafted world, with tight yet open-ended environments. Whichever path you take, there'll always be something around the corner, waiting to be discovered.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2060790/extras/